Diwali of this year has come at my door&lt;br&gt;
I am ready to go out&lt;br&gt;
To Light the lamp on the outside of walls of my house.&lt;br&gt;
To search those whom I lost in 365 days.&lt;br&gt;
To invite those who went away from me&lt;br&gt;
To share the sweets prepared by sweet keeper&lt;br&gt;
To share the gift and to give the warmth.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
